eb.org/2024/01/28/crouton-net/ )\r\n\r\nBut what else is there? What are some of the silly fun sites you know about? It doesn't need to make sense. Just.. Fun. Whimsy.","submitter_user":"Aks","user_is_author":true,"tags":["ask","web"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ncngka","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ncngka/what_fun_websites_do_you_know"},{"short_id":"k3delj","created_at":"2026-05-02T11:34:51.000-05:00","title":"Agentic Coding is Burning Me Out","url":"https://0xsid.com/blog/agentic-coding-fatigue","score":7,"flags":0,"comment_count":3,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"deejayy","user_is_author":false,"tags":["programming","vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/k3delj","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/k3delj/agentic_coding_is_burning_me_out"},{"short_id":"areye8","created_at":"2026-05-02T11:26:40.000-05:00","title":"An ansible playbook to mitigate the copy-fail vulnerability","url":"https://gist.github.com/crodjer/9726b30887a9e2ed37ad2d0385bd5b91","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"\u003cp\u003eSince algif_aead is implicated in the exploit, I created an ansible playbook which blacklists algif_aead if nothing's referring to it to avoid any potential exploits. None of my machines were actively using it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eExtracted this single playbook out as a gist in case you also have multiple machines to quickly patch.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Since algif_aead is implicated in the exploit, I created an ansible playbook which blacklists algif_aead if nothing's referring to it to avoid any potential exploits. None of my machines were actively using it.\r\n\r\nExtracted this single playbook out as a gist in case you also have multiple machines to quickly patch.","submitter_user":"crodjer","user_is_author":true,"tags":["linux","security"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/areye8","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/areye8/ansible_playbook_mitigate_copy_fail"},{"short_id":"pcrlu